    <p>As Elizabeth <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="had no longer any interest of her own to pursue"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(再也没有什么自己感兴趣的事想要探究)</code></b>, she turned her attention almost entirely on her sister and Mr. Bingley, and <b data-toggle="tooltip" data-original-title="the train of agreeable reflections"><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">________(一连串心情舒畅的想法)</code></b> which her observations gave birth to, made her perhaps almost as happy as Jane.</p>
